{"tid":2301774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門教職員涉潛內聯網竊學生資料被捕","createTime":"2020-11-26T14:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T14:43:24.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fabe6e065ec8b53c00711c2591089bffa64226a","tid":2301774,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:28:39.000Z","msg":"唔係走去媾學生啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月28日屯門區一間學校報案稱，校方收到學生及家長舉報<strong><span class=\"red\">一名學校男職員曾在校內會見多名學生，及後私下致電他們</span></strong>，引起關注。屯門警區人員經深入調查後，相信該名男職員於今年8月至10月期間，多次以校外電腦登入學校內聯網，在未獲授權下瀏覽及取得多名學生個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201126/PDNG6M3J4FG4HKMNIEEWPPPZHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201126%2FPDNG6M3J4FG4HKMNIEEWPPPZHY%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=96bfa32f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201126%2FPDNG6M3J4FG4HKMNIEEWPPPZHY%2F&h=cd90aeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201126/PDNG6M3J4FG4HKMNIEEWPPPZHY/</a>"},{"pid":"b6835f0a5d8e790a1311ba0ff74499babc7592db","tid":2301774,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im